title: Lilyhammer S2 Ep3 - Welcome To The Mountains
description:
Lilyhammer S2 Ep3 - Welcome To The Mountains

Welcome To The Mountains - Roy's el-scooter for the disabled is blown to bits. The hit is accompanied with a note from the British gangsters, who want a meet where they can be compensated for the car. While Frank is preparing for the meeting, Sigrid dumps the twins on him, announcing that it is his turn to care for them the whole month, given the "papyperm" as required by Norwegian law. So Frank brings the twins to the meeting with the gangsters. 

From Norway, in Norwegian 

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
